# Altura Documentation Portfolio

This repo showcases a project document I wrote for Altura Trade.  
The document focuses on explaining the platform clearly for users and founders, not engineers.

**Role:** Technical writer / content creator  
**Audience:** Founders, traders, and general users  
**Purpose:** Clear platform documentation, easy to understand, highlighting features and processes

## View the Document

You can view the document here: [Altura Docs](https://docs.altura.trade/)
